name: Shaker_Series_48-inch_Natural_Finish_On_The_Wall_Cabinet
reviews: More expensive than other cabinets for storage, but they are made totally of solid wood! And the idea and the use of space with these is just magic. I bought two of them, one for the upstairs hallway, and one for the adjacent SMALL bathroom which had no storage space. Wish I could afford two more. They are just wonderful - period.
description:
Ideal as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet, or storage cabinet anywhere the Shaker Series wall cabinet is the perfect choice. This cabinet mounts on the wall with built-in cleats inside for an easy installation.
Four (4) fully adjustable glass shelvesConcealed hingesDoors are left undrilled for a knob or handle so you can mount them to open either directionPerfect as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet, or storage cabinet anywhereBuilt-in cleats for an easy installationSolid maple doorsMaterials: Wood/glassFinish: Natural pine, can be painted or stainedInside cabinet depth: 7.25 inchesDimensions: 49.5 inches high x 15.25 inches wide x 8 inches deep MaterialWoodTypeWall CabinetFinishNatural Finish
